## Credentials file:

api_key=

api_secret=

bearer=

access_token=

access_token_secret=

user_id=<numerical user id>

handle=<actual user ID> 



<b>No empty spaces between each field.</b>


## Quotes file:

Begin all quotes on their own line
Begin all quotes with ^

### Example:

^This is quote number 1

^This is the second quote

^Quotes can be long and take up multiple lines. The script will separate quotes by the character at the beginning. Quotes can be as long as you want them to be. The script can post multi-tweet threads. 

^This is the 4th quote